Package: phylosamp
Type: Package
Title: Tools to calculate the probability of transmission given phylogenetic linkage
Version: 0.1.2
Authors@R: c(person("John R", "Giles", role=c("aut", "cre"), email="giles@jhu.edu"),
              person("Shirlee", "Wohl", role=c("aut"), email="swohl@jhu.edu"),
              person("Justin", "Lessler", role=c("aut"), email="justin@jhu.edu"))
Maintainer: Justin Lessler <justin@jhu.edu>
Description: Implements novel tools that estimate the probability of true transmission between two cases given 
    phylogenetic linkage and the expected number of true transmission links in a sample.
License: GPL-2
URL: https://github.com/HopkinsIDD/phylosamp
BugReports: https://https://github.com/HopkinsIDD/phylosamp/issues
